refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public DateInterval::__construct stringinterval_spec
Crea un nuevo objeto DateInterval.

&reftitle.examples;
Ejemplo de DateInterval
<?php
$intervalo = new DateInterval('P2Y4DT6H8M'); print_r($intervalo);
?>
&example.outputs;
DateInterval Object ( [y] => 2 [m] => 0 [d] => 4 [h] => 6 [i] => 8 [s] => 0 [invert] => 0 [days] => 0 )
